{"s":"church-vinyl-banner","img":"vinyl-banner.jpg","badge":"Best Seller","cat":"Banners & Flags","name":"Church Vinyl Banner","tag":"Heavy-duty outdoor banners crafted for your ministry.","verse":"Go and make disciples of all nations","ref":"Matthew 28:19","specs":[("Material","510g PVC Vinyl"),("Print","UV Ink, 1440 dpi"),("UV Resistance","Up to 5 years"),("Finishing","Double-sewn + metal grommets"),("Max Width","5 meters")],"feats":["Cross, dove & scripture designs available","Weatherproof — rain, sun, wind resistant","Metal grommets at all corners","Full-color 1440 dpi printing","Rush production for Sunday deadlines"],"desc":["Church Vinyl Banners are our most popular product. Whether announcing a revival, welcoming visitors, promoting VBS, or sharing a scripture verse, a well-designed vinyl banner is one of the most effective tools your ministry can have.","Our 510g premium vinyl is UV-cured to stay vibrant for up to 5 years outdoors. Each banner has double-folded sewn edges and metal grommets for secure mounting anywhere — poles, fences, or building facades.","Every banner can be customized with crosses, doves, praying hands, and scripture text. Upload your own design or let our team create something that represents your congregation."],"uc":[("⛪","Sunday service announcements"),("📖","Scripture & message banners"),("🎉","VBS, revival & special events"),("🌟","Holiday & seasonal displays"),("🤝","Community outreach programs"),("🏫","Youth ministry")],"sizes":["2x4 ft","3x6 ft","4x8 ft","4x10 ft","Custom"]},
{"s":"mesh-banner","img":"mesh-banner.jpg","badge":"Outdoor","cat":"Banners & Flags","name":"Wind-Resistant Mesh Banner","tag":"Breathable mesh banners for fences, outdoor stages, and revival tents.","verse":"The wind blows where it wishes","ref":"John 3:8","specs":[("Material","300-380gsm Vinyl Mesh"),("Print","Eco-Solvent, 1440 dpi"),("UV Resistance","1-3 years"),("Wind Resistance","30-40% open mesh"),("Finishing","Double-sewn + grommets")],"feats":["Airflow through mesh — won't act as a sail","Perfect for chain-link fences at church events","Available in 300gsm and 380gsm weights","Metal grommets at regular intervals","Great for revivals, tent events, and fairs"],"desc":["Mesh banners are the smart choice for outdoor signage in windy conditions. Unlike solid vinyl, the open mesh structure lets wind pass through — preventing the banner from acting as a sail and reducing stress on mounting points.","Ideal for chain-link fences around your church property, scaffolding, outdoor events, or the perimeter of revival tents. Still provides bold, clear visuals from a distance while handling wind gracefully.","We offer 300gsm for lighter-duty applications and 380gsm for more permanent installations. All mesh banners include metal grommets and double-sewn edges as standard."],"uc":[("⛺","Revival tent perimeter signage"),("🏗️","Scaffolding & construction wraps"),("🏟️","Event fencing & barriers"),("🌬️","High-wind outdoor locations"),("🤝","Community outreach events"),("⛪","Church parking lot displays")],"sizes":["3x6 ft","4x8 ft","4x20 ft","Custom"]},
{"s":"fabric-sanctuary-banner","img":"fabric-banner.jpg","badge":"Indoor","cat":"Banners & Flags","name":"Fabric Sanctuary Banner","tag":"Elegant indoor fabric banners for worship spaces.","verse":"Praise Him in His sanctuary","ref":"Psalm 150:1","specs":[("Material","250gsm Polyester Fabric"),("Print","Thermal Sublimation"),("UV Resistance","3-6 months indoor"),("Finish","Soft — no glare"),("Hanging","Rod pocket or grommets")],"feats":["Soft fabric — elegant for sanctuaries","No light glare — perfect for photography","Vibrant thermal sublimation printing","Cross, dove, flame, stained-glass designs","Lightweight — ideal for traveling ministries"],"desc":["Fabric Sanctuary Banners bring a different kind of presence to your worship space. Unlike vinyl, fabric has a soft, dignified look that suits the reverence of a sanctuary. These banners drape beautifully and photograph without any glare.","Using thermal sublimation printing, we achieve vibrant full-color imagery that becomes part of the fabric itself — it will not peel, crack, or fade under normal indoor conditions.","Popular designs include crosses with rays of light, descending doves, flames representing the Holy Spirit, stained-glass patterns, and scripture passages in elegant typography."],"uc":[("⛪","Behind the pulpit / altar"),("🕊️","Sanctuary wall décor"),("📸","Photography backdrops"),("🎄","Seasonal worship decorations"),("✈️","Traveling ministries"),("🎭","Baptism & ceremony backdrops")],"sizes":["2x4 ft","2x6 ft","3x6 ft","4x8 ft","Custom"]},
{"s":"custom-ministry-flag","img":"flag.jpg","badge":"Custom","cat":"Banners & Flags","name":"Custom Ministry Flag","tag":"Fly your faith — custom flags for churches and ministries.","verse":"As for me and my house, we will serve the Lord","ref":"Joshua 24:15","specs":[("Material","75D or 100D Polyester"),("Standard Size","3x5 ft"),("Print","Full-color"),("Sides","Single or double-sided"),("Header","Canvas + brass grommets")],"feats":["Feature your church logo, cross, or ministry crest","Available in 3x5ft or any custom size","Durable polyester for outdoor use","Double-sided printing available","Canvas header with brass grommets"],"desc":["A custom ministry flag is one of the most visible statements of identity your church can make. Whether flown from a pole outside your building, carried in a processional, or used at outdoor crusades, a flag bearing your church emblem broadcasts your mission with dignity.","We print on 75D or 100D polyester — a durable, weather-resistant fabric that holds color well and flies cleanly in the wind. Standard size is 3x5ft, but we produce any size you need.","For ministries wanting visibility from both sides — processional or event flags — we offer double-sided printing with a center liner to prevent show-through."],"uc":[("🏛️","Flagpole outside church"),("🎺","Processional & worship flags"),("⛺","Outdoor crusades & revivals"),("🏅","Ministry events & conferences"),("🏫","Christian schools"),("🌍","Mission trips")],"sizes":["3x5 ft","4x6 ft","5x8 ft","Custom"]},
{"s":"feather-teardrop-flag","img":"feather-flag.jpg","badge":"Event Favorite","cat":"Banners & Flags","name":"Feather & Teardrop Flag","tag":"Eye-catching swooper flags that draw crowds to your outdoor events.","verse":"Stand firm in the freedom Christ has set you free","ref":"Galatians 5:1","specs":[("Shapes","Feather, Teardrop, Rectangular"),("Heights","2.8m to 5.5m"),("Material","Polyester Fabric"),("Print","Full-color"),("Base","Spike, Cross base, or Water base")],"feats":["6 height options from 2.8m to 5.5m","Feather, teardrop, and rectangular shapes","Ground spike for grass installation","Cross base for indoor or hard surfaces","Lightweight — no tools needed for assembly"],"desc":["Feather and teardrop flags are designed to be noticed. Their distinctive curved shapes create movement in even the lightest breeze, drawing the eye from a distance and signaling that something is happening at your location.","Perfect for outdoor events — place them along the sidewalk before a revival, flank your ministry tent at a festival, or line the entrance to your church for special services. Visible up to 5.5 meters tall.","Each flag comes with a fiberglass pole and your choice of base: a ground spike for grass, or a cross base for indoor and hard surface use. Assembly takes under a minute with no tools."],"uc":[("🎪","Event & festival entrances"),("⛺","Revival & crusade perimeter"),("🛒","Sidewalk & parking lot draws"),("🏟️","Sports ministry events"),("🎄","Holiday & seasonal services"),("📢","Community outreach")],"sizes":["2.8m","3.4m","4.0m","4.5m","5.0m","5.5m"]},
